tags: please i spent most of last night crying about this
body:
I messed up Real Bad

I accidentally deleted my two videos that I took before my Interactive Introverts show (July 29th, St. Louis Missouri). The only one I really want back is the one I took during the audience singing “Welcome to the Black Parade” because it was one of the happiest and safest-feeling moments of my life…

I know it’s a long shot, but does anyone have a video of the audience at Interactive Introverts singing with “Welcome to the Black Parade”? Honestly it doesn’t have to be St. Louis, any of the shows will do
